# HEADING

A README.MD is a file that introduces and explains a project. Hence, it is important that it is easily understood by everyone that comes across it.

Heading : A heading is an important part of a markdown file.
To add a heading to your README.md, do this;
> \# HEADING

To add a second or third heading; 
> \## SECOND HEADING

>\### THIRD HEADING

The '#' (hashtag symbol) followed by the heading of choice.